snippet.title: The Psychology of Amber Heard. PART 1.
snippet.description:
#AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp #JusticeForJohnnyDepp
In this video I attempt to discuss and explain Amber Heards erratic behavior. 

While Amber is a horrible human being for what she has done, I do hope that she gets the mental help she needs. No I am not a Professional. This is my first video on the whole situation, the quality will become better.
Also wanna address that I made some stupid grammar mistakes. The auto correct for my editing software was not working at the time.

Heard allegedly did all of these things. I think many of us agree she wanted to hurt Depp. 

Disclaimer: All of my videos from here and in the future are all alleged. I am not trying to defame anyone.
